data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bath home, built in 2019, boasts ceramic tile, recessed lighting, and updated kitchen fixtures. The spacious living room seamlessly connects to a well-appointed kitchen featuring custom cabinets, granite countertops, a large eat-at island with a sink, and stainless steel appliances. The master suite offers a double vanity, soaking tub, and a separate walk-in shower. A versatile office/den serves as an optional 4th bedroom. Outside, you'll find a custom covered patio running the length of the home, a privacy fence, automatic sprinklers, and a spacious yard. Plus, a custom railing adorns the front patio. Don't miss the community's fantastic pool and park amenities! This home is sparkling clean and ready to show!
